g/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993353</a><br />\n<br />\n支那01帶風向同滲透已經延伸到連登外面 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家訓醒未</span></span><br />\n立法會選戰 連登仔第一個考驗：打柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LD7dnxE.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知道點解今次中共病毒疫情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共派政黨</span></span></strong>，特別係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>，民意得分直線上升???<br />\n答案：係因為支那01係背後緊搞鬼！！<br />\n『<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200428-chi&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=1fa7befe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi</a><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">民研計劃於四月中由真實訪問員以隨機抽樣電話訪問方式，分兩階段成功訪問了506和500名香港居民。最新政治團體民望調查顯示，對比七個月前，以熟悉程度計，首3位最多巿民認識的政治團體分別是民建聯、民主黨和公民黨，而民協則取代民陣重新上榜。論支持度評分，香港眾志以43.1分首次奪得首位；第二至六位是民主黨、民協、人民力量、公民黨和社民連，分別得42.9、41.6、40.0、39.4及39.0分；自由黨、民建聯、工聯會和新民黨分別排第七至十位，得37.7、35.2、32.0及29.7分。市民對排名首五位政治團體的平均分為41.4分，而首十位則為38.1分。公民黨的評分較七個月前顯著下跌5.7分，是其於2006年上榜以來的新低，</span></em>而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯則顯著上升8.4分。</span></span>』<br />\n<br />\n2020.04.24 損人不利己並非為政之道<br />\nWHAT THE FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刻意放大公民黨郭榮鏗 「阻住晒」「影響民生，議會運作」的負面形象<br />\n堅守議會 減慢赤化速度 阻止23條立法絕口不提<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330694038183350272.jpeg/xOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330694038183350272.jpeg%2FxOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6337beae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01"},{"pid":"9176021c80a7789d42adebe9a46a721c670292fd","tid":1993361,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfbb4dc5edb99896f026a43dd7b2fe5ed3b28e51","tid":1993361,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993353</a><br />\n<br />\n支那01帶風向同滲透已經延伸到連登外面 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家訓醒未</span></span><br />\n立法會選戰 連登仔第一個考驗：打柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LD7dnxE.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知道點解今次中共病毒疫情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共派政黨</span></span></strong>，特別係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>，民意得分直線上升???<br />\n答案：係因為支那01係背後緊搞鬼！！<br />\n『<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200428-chi&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=1fa7befe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi</a><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">民研計劃於四月中由真實訪問員以隨機抽樣電話訪問方式，分兩階段成功訪問了506和500名香港居民。最新政治團體民望調查顯示，對比七個月前，以熟悉程度計，首3位最多巿民認識的政治團體分別是民建聯、民主黨和公民黨，而民協則取代民陣重新上榜。論支持度評分，香港眾志以43.1分首次奪得首位；第二至六位是民主黨、民協、人民力量、公民黨和社民連，分別得42.9、41.6、40.0、39.4及39.0分；自由黨、民建聯、工聯會和新民黨分別排第七至十位，得37.7、35.2、32.0及29.7分。市民對排名首五位政治團體的平均分為41.4分，而首十位則為38.1分。公民黨的評分較七個月前顯著下跌5.7分，是其於2006年上榜以來的新低，</span></em>而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯則顯著上升8.4分。</span></span>』<br />\n<br />\n2020.04.24 損人不利己並非為政之道<br />\nWHAT THE FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刻意放大公民黨郭榮鏗 「阻住晒」「影響民生，議會運作」的負面形象<br />\n堅守議會 減慢赤化速度 阻止23條立法絕口不提<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330694038183350272.jpeg/xOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330694038183350272.jpeg%2FxOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6337beae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"pined"},{"pid":"128b9d96e80238e750eba66aab8e248b0a7b8b85","tid":1993361,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9176021c80a7789d42adebe9a46a721c670292fd","tid":1993361,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfbb4dc5edb99896f026a43dd7b2fe5ed3b28e51","tid":1993361,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－<br />\n【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\"